The consciousness research is the buried bomb. "Multiple cognitive signatures in one vessel." Plant it. Don't water it.
Track what Davinia reads. Ismara absorbs everything. The Crown is getting smarter.
Saijah's migraine going quiet is significant. Relief AND severance.
Alfonso's quarantine is the LIVING VESSEL experiment ΓÇö the third vessel type. The Cognitorium tried machines (GEAR ΓÇö worked), crystals (Matrix ΓÇö worked), and biology (Quarantine 7 ΓÇö failed). The city's sterilization system (which Alfonso discovers upstairs) is the baseline: the Dwemer could keep biology OUT perfectly. The quarantine is where they deliberately put biology IN and it exploded. The failure was specifically about incompatible tonal frequencies in living flesh ΓÇö the exact problem Hjolmar diagnosed in Alfonso. If he can't harmonize Namira and Peryite, what's in that scorched pod is his future.
Kyboh's gauntlet prototype is in the Cognitorium, not the city. It's research equipment ΓÇö the ancestor of his bone enchantment. GEAR can explain its purpose. "Vessel Interface" is the most important project name Kyboh will hear until the Echo Mimic arc begins.

